WEBVTT

00:00.024 --> 00:04.972
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

00:05.944 --> 00:08.652
♪ My heart is racing ♪

00:09.784 --> 00:13.792
♪ The world has fallen silent ♪

00:13.816 --> 00:18.572
♪ Hey, when I imagine you ♪

00:19.608 --> 00:22.636
♪ What kind of look ♪

00:23.640 --> 00:27.584
♪ Attracted me to you ♪

00:27.608 --> 00:30.880
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:30.904 --> 00:34.368
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:34.392 --> 00:39.640
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:39.640 --> 00:41.258
♪ I love you ♪

00:41.258 --> 00:44.736
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:44.760 --> 00:48.032
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

00:48.056 --> 00:53.728
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

00:53.752 --> 00:55.096
♪ I love you ♪

00:55.096 --> 00:58.432
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

00:58.456 --> 01:01.804
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:01.912 --> 01:07.109
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:07.109 --> 01:08.792
♪ I love you ♪

01:08.792 --> 01:12.192
♪ Slowly, slowly, we fall in love ♪

01:12.216 --> 01:15.616
♪ Slowly, slowly, I can't leave you ♪

01:15.640 --> 01:21.216
♪ Slowly, slowly, I am with you ♪

01:21.240 --> 01:24.652
♪ I love you ♪

01:26.930 --> 01:27.720
=Love Me, Love My Voice=

01:27.720 --> 01:30.780
=Love Me, Love My Voice=
=Episode 29=

01:31.368 --> 01:34.076
(What do you think
is behind the island?)

01:36.956 --> 01:39.577
Mr. Qiang, go for it!

01:48.277 --> 01:49.337
Right,

01:50.077 --> 01:51.697
I just thought of something.

01:53.956 --> 01:56.700
How will you spend
your National Holiday?

01:57.224 --> 02:00.176
National Holiday?
I haven't thought about it.

02:01.836 --> 02:05.053
I'll have a seminar in Qiandao Lake
for the first four days.

02:05.077 --> 02:09.936
If you are not doing anything,
come to Qiandao Lake with us.

02:10.556 --> 02:13.616
Sure. Qiandao Lake.

02:13.676 --> 02:17.016
- I haven't been there yet.
- That's a deal then.

02:19.917 --> 02:22.932
Last time I told my parents
that I was in Yangshuo for business.

02:22.956 --> 02:30.056
How should I tell my parents this time?
They are quite strict.

02:31.917 --> 02:35.412
I met your grandfather. If needed,

02:35.436 --> 02:38.216
I can arrange for my parents to meet
your parents.

02:40.716 --> 02:42.097
I'm serious.

02:44.516 --> 02:49.577
No need. I'll think of a way.

02:50.597 --> 02:52.216
By myself.

02:52.716 --> 02:54.216
Myself.

03:02.152 --> 03:04.157
(Wangjia Supermarket)

03:04.157 --> 03:08.092
Okay, I can go together with you.
So that your parents can rest assured.

03:08.116 --> 03:11.692
- Who dares to act out when I'm there?
- What are you talking about?

03:11.716 --> 03:13.293
Mr. Mo has nothing to hide.

03:13.317 --> 03:15.516
He will act properly
even though you are not there.

03:15.516 --> 03:18.377
Fine, you are always right.

03:18.556 --> 03:21.492
The Perfect Voice Studio appreciated it
a lot that you treated them with snacks.

03:21.516 --> 03:23.548
We can go together if you are available.

03:24.157 --> 03:27.692
I didn't say yes for you.
I'm afraid you already have plans.

03:27.716 --> 03:31.013
- No, I don't have any plan.
- Look at you.

03:31.037 --> 03:33.037
Show some of the spirit you use on me
and be proud for once.

03:33.037 --> 03:35.752
Say you need to go home.

03:35.752 --> 03:38.012
I'm never proud
when facing brilliant people.

03:38.888 --> 03:42.532
Sheng, when will you leave?
Let me know. I will check the tickets.

03:42.556 --> 03:46.016
We will buy tickets together
and settle the money later.

03:46.357 --> 03:49.613
Thank them for me. I'll definitely go.

03:49.637 --> 03:52.257
- Got it.
- I'm going to work now.

03:54.037 --> 03:58.477
Sheng, I can go for you.
So the money for the hotel and plane...

03:58.477 --> 04:02.736
How can you be so shameless?
You go out and let your sister pay?

04:02.811 --> 04:06.907
Fine, I'll reluctantly pay myself

04:06.931 --> 04:10.907
to go enjoy a holiday
with the one you admire.

04:10.931 --> 04:14.548
Others can't get this kind of chance,
and you are picky about it.

04:14.572 --> 04:18.712
- I don't know him. That's your idol.
- Alright, get off.

04:23.931 --> 04:28.827
(May all the people in Chaisang
never leave their families like me.)

04:28.851 --> 04:33.671
- (May all soldiers guard rivers...)
- This speech is so touching.

04:33.731 --> 04:39.240
- Right?
- (May we expel the outsiders one day)

04:39.240 --> 04:42.792
- Your phone's ringing.
- (and forever eliminate warfare.)

04:42.792 --> 04:44.284
Your phone is ringing.

04:48.008 --> 04:49.820
(Zhou Zheng)

04:53.308 --> 04:56.209
You continue. I'll take a call.

05:02.868 --> 05:06.209
- Hello?
- Hey, long time no see.

05:07.988 --> 05:14.769
Not that long. My roommates and I
went to see your show last time.

05:14.988 --> 05:16.889
We've kind of met then.

05:18.428 --> 05:20.889
How would you spend your holiday?

05:25.589 --> 05:28.808
- I have no idea.
- Then what about we spend it together?

05:28.988 --> 05:31.844
The Top Three in Perfect Voice
are excellent.

05:31.868 --> 05:34.368
Look at Juemei, so good-shaped.

05:37.509 --> 05:40.889
Another flower high upon the ridges.
I wonder who will get him.

05:48.668 --> 05:52.969
- Uh, I...
- Thank your friend for me.

06:11.988 --> 06:13.529
Still feel regretful?

06:14.920 --> 06:16.156
Am I?

06:16.748 --> 06:20.649
You didn't even eat.
You may fool others but not me.

06:22.748 --> 06:26.524
I'm not upset.

06:26.548 --> 06:32.808
It's just Perfect Voice hosts this event
and Mr. Qiang will withdraw.

06:32.988 --> 06:36.368
I feel pity that I can't participate in.

06:36.668 --> 06:42.684
But I feel happy Off Key can be there.
Anyway, newcomers can take over.

06:43.228 --> 06:44.969
You grow up.

06:45.988 --> 06:48.060
Now showing the demeanor of the elder.

06:48.188 --> 06:52.009
It's as if you're so much older
and I'm so much younger.

06:52.389 --> 06:54.449
- I don't eat.
- Don't eat?

06:55.469 --> 06:57.644
I was gonna share some delicious food
from the fridge with you.

06:57.668 --> 07:00.529
- Forget about it.
- No, don't forget it.

07:00.668 --> 07:03.488
It's my fault.

07:03.589 --> 07:06.608
- What? I can't hear you.
- My fault.

07:15.188 --> 07:21.209
- The braised duck legs made by my dad.
- That's my favorite.

07:21.308 --> 07:23.204
- Especially made for me?
- Of course!

07:23.228 --> 07:25.125
He asked me to take it cuz you love it.

07:25.149 --> 07:27.685
Last night he didn't let me
eat a lot to save them for you.

07:27.709 --> 07:31.128
Say thanks to him for me.
He is like my half dad.

07:31.389 --> 07:37.524
No, if one day you fall in love with me.
Then he would be my father-in-law.

07:37.548 --> 07:41.644
- My dad doesn't have that fortune.
- Stop that. I don't have that fortune.

07:41.668 --> 07:44.885
- Your parents are so kind.
- That's her parents.

07:44.909 --> 07:47.084
That won't make Doudou
fall in love with you.

07:47.108 --> 07:51.009
I don't expect her to like me.
I just want braised duck legs.

07:51.428 --> 07:52.649
Eat.

08:01.308 --> 08:03.148
What? Are you in love with me?

08:03.148 --> 08:06.368
Don't smile so sweet,
or I may confess to you.

08:09.108 --> 08:10.889
Doudou, come back.

08:12.469 --> 08:16.644
Mr. Mo will have a meeting next week
and he lets us go together to have fun.

08:16.668 --> 08:18.588
You can organize it.

08:18.909 --> 08:22.928
- Why you two don't do it?
- Let me help you.

08:23.588 --> 08:26.885
Let him help you. I might not go.

08:26.909 --> 08:30.529
I can only take a day off for holiday.
I will see how it goes.

08:30.828 --> 08:33.409
You can only take one day off?

08:34.149 --> 08:36.328
No choice. We're short-staffed.

08:37.708 --> 08:40.289
What, do you want me to go?

08:43.188 --> 08:46.108
Everyone wants you to go.
Everyone should be there.

08:46.708 --> 08:47.848
I'll try.

08:56.168 --> 08:59.277
♪ Meteor flies to the edge of the sky ♪

08:59.301 --> 09:01.526
♪ Crossing the horizon ♪

09:02.184 --> 09:04.712
♪ The wind listens to all the wishes ♪

09:04.712 --> 09:07.103
♪ Fluttering memories ♪

09:07.944 --> 09:10.149
♪ Sunshine through the dancing leaves ♪

09:10.149 --> 09:13.924
- Qiandao Lake, we are coming!
- So beautiful!

09:13.948 --> 09:17.205
- Wake up.
- Friends behind, catch up. Hurry!

09:17.229 --> 09:19.489
- Come on!
- Let's go!

09:19.749 --> 09:25.269
- Hurry, overtake them.
- Overtake them.

09:25.269 --> 09:27.891
♪ Dreams can reach the other shore ♪

09:28.188 --> 09:29.125
Hurry up!

09:29.149 --> 09:32.208
Overtake them. Let's go!

09:36.029 --> 09:39.184
- Feeling refreshed, right?
- Must be.

09:39.208 --> 09:42.024
♪ Every moment of falling in love ♪

09:42.024 --> 09:44.631
♪ Let it blossom ♪

09:52.509 --> 09:56.524
- How about you sit closer? It's dangerous.
- Okay.

09:56.548 --> 09:57.568
Okay.

10:01.308 --> 10:05.532
What are they doing?
What are they talking about?

10:06.120 --> 10:07.729
Stop looking.

10:08.789 --> 10:12.324
- You are Sheng's cousin, right?
- Yeah, I am her fifth cousin.

10:12.348 --> 10:14.845
- She has five cousins?
- Yeah, I am the fifth.

10:14.869 --> 10:17.208
So are you a couple?

10:17.548 --> 10:21.208
- She is my employee and I'm her boss.
- My boss, boss.

10:21.308 --> 10:23.568
- We have no relationship.
- Yeah, no relationship.

10:29.509 --> 10:30.765
Well,

10:30.789 --> 10:33.049
if there's anything you want to eat,
drink, or play,

10:33.049 --> 10:35.289
just let me know.
I'm familiar with here.

10:35.588 --> 10:37.845
Feishao, aren't you from Ancheng?

10:37.869 --> 10:40.649
When did your family's business
expand to Qiandao Lake?

10:40.749 --> 10:44.444
You are truly a businessman.
You even guessed this.

10:44.468 --> 10:46.556
Do you have any recommendations?

10:46.918 --> 10:50.924
Off-roaders and hot air balloons,
have you tried? They're available here.

10:50.948 --> 10:52.725
Off-roaders? On the island?

10:52.749 --> 10:56.885
Yes, in the mud. It's thrilling.
I play it every time I come here.

10:56.909 --> 10:58.725
No more rolling?

10:58.749 --> 11:02.249
- Can we go and try this?
- I will go with you if you want to.

11:07.229 --> 11:08.229
Sleepy?

11:09.548 --> 11:12.738
Yesterday, I had to do both
recording songs and live streaming.

11:12.738 --> 11:14.588
I didn't even get two hours of sleep.

11:14.588 --> 11:18.609
- Get some sleep as we get to the hotel.
- Then the whole morning would be wasted.

11:19.548 --> 11:23.129
Sleep first to have the energy
to have fun, right?

11:48.828 --> 11:52.548
How's it, everybody?
The environment is quite nice, isn't it?

11:52.548 --> 11:55.489
- Must be!
- Wang, keep low key.

11:56.389 --> 12:00.548
Guys, the place isn't inferior to that
Zhu organized in Yangshuo, is it?

12:00.548 --> 12:02.284
- Better.
- Much better.

12:02.308 --> 12:04.684
- Not bad.
- I booked all the three buildings.

12:04.708 --> 12:08.684
One with two floors, for four.
Let me make the arrangement.

12:08.708 --> 12:13.684
Mr. Mo, you two stay in this building.
It's more peaceful for a couple.

12:13.708 --> 12:16.044
- Xiaoxing, stay with me.
- Sure.

12:16.068 --> 12:18.284
- Xiaoxing, get the room card.
- Then I will stay with Mr. Mo.

12:18.308 --> 12:20.649
No, no, no, I need to stay
with my sister.

12:21.468 --> 12:24.765
I'm in an unfamiliar place, so awkward.
Can you stay with me?

12:24.789 --> 12:26.509
I'm no less unfamiliar with this
place than you are.

12:26.509 --> 12:28.968
Yiru, we can share a bed.
We four stay together.

12:28.968 --> 12:30.149
- Yes, you stay with us.
- Alright.

12:30.149 --> 12:32.468
Come on, cut the crap.
You live in this building.

12:32.468 --> 12:33.668
- Come on.
- Room card, room card.

12:33.668 --> 12:34.588
- Give me.
- That way.

12:34.588 --> 12:36.828
- Come with us.
- This way, this way.

12:36.828 --> 12:38.804
- Room 932.
- Let's go.

12:38.828 --> 12:40.365
- Hurry up.
- You come with us.

12:40.389 --> 12:42.924
- Let's go, brothers.
- Let's go, guys.

12:42.948 --> 12:45.729
We are the four single wolves
in the wind.

12:47.948 --> 12:49.729
- Be careful.
- It's ok. Let me do it.

12:53.509 --> 12:56.609
- Xiaoxing, we choose the second floor.
- Sure.

12:57.229 --> 12:58.668
Sure, come on.

12:58.668 --> 13:01.005
- What about the luggages?
- I'll help you carry it.

13:01.029 --> 13:02.848
- Let's go.
- Go upstairs to see.

13:09.548 --> 13:11.649
The view is so charming, Sheng.

13:11.869 --> 13:13.668
- A big forest.
- I'll place the luggages here.

13:13.668 --> 13:15.404
- Call us if you need help.
- Thanks.

13:15.428 --> 13:17.489
Thanks, thanks, thanks.

13:21.308 --> 13:25.965
Sheng, I'll take a shower and have a rest.
I felt too excited yesterday to sleep.

13:25.989 --> 13:26.989
Okay.

13:29.029 --> 13:32.485
- You just lie here in such a good day?
- Tired.

13:32.509 --> 13:34.168
So comfortable!

13:34.588 --> 13:37.009
Mr. Mo, where are we going
in the afternoon?

13:37.708 --> 13:39.249
No idea yet.

13:40.149 --> 13:41.564
I'll go get you some drinks.

13:41.588 --> 13:44.249
- I want coke.
- Me too, thanks.

13:45.188 --> 13:50.324
- You won't go out?
- Sleepy. I was on duty last night.

13:50.348 --> 13:52.605
I'm embarrassed

13:52.629 --> 13:55.765
to sleep with Gu Sheng's brother
on one large double bed.

13:55.789 --> 13:59.448
I would rather do sunbathe outside.

14:00.509 --> 14:02.409
Why is Mu also asleep?

14:03.428 --> 14:07.684
He had a parents' meeting yesterday.
Lots of parents talked to him.

14:07.708 --> 14:11.848
After coming home, his mom
talked about dating with him.

14:11.989 --> 14:16.845
And his sister woke him up to talk
because she has pressure on study.

14:16.869 --> 14:18.404
That really wore him out.

14:18.428 --> 14:22.688
- How come you know everything?
- He complained the whole way.

14:33.909 --> 14:37.485
- Do you want to see the lake?
- Not in a hurry.

14:37.509 --> 14:39.968
You said you are sleepy. So sleep first.

14:41.789 --> 14:44.889
I don't want
to waste three days sleeping.

14:46.828 --> 14:51.088
I've gone on long journeys
with you twice.

14:54.348 --> 14:56.168
It's my great honor.

15:06.149 --> 15:09.289
Sheng, do you want some drinks?

15:11.348 --> 15:12.889
No, thank you.

15:19.948 --> 15:25.409
I'll go change into clean clothes.
I've been sitting in the car all day.

16:23.468 --> 16:27.048
Juemei went out for a walk.
You can stay in my room for a while.

16:28.789 --> 16:29.789
Let's go.

16:36.109 --> 16:37.289
Sleepy?

16:38.188 --> 16:43.088
Little. Xiaoxing occupied the whole
bed when sleeping upstairs.

16:44.269 --> 16:46.968
Maybe you can rest a little in bed
and then we can go out.

16:56.308 --> 17:00.169
Don't you feel tired after all the
meetings? Do you want to sleep a little?

17:00.388 --> 17:01.564
I'm fine.

17:02.068 --> 17:06.445
We're out for a vacation, after all.
Sleep if you're tired, and go out later.

17:06.469 --> 17:08.848
You sleep. I'll read books for a while.

17:38.587 --> 17:43.695
♪ Which sound soaks the green plums ♪

17:44.539 --> 17:49.487
♪ Which sound wrinkles the blue sky ♪

17:50.417 --> 17:54.706
♪ Shedding an invisible spring rain ♪

17:54.706 --> 18:00.905
♪ The world is drunk at a timid moment ♪

18:02.231 --> 18:07.599
♪ We talk and laugh
as if we are holding hands ♪

18:08.539 --> 18:14.587
♪ We stay silent
like falling behind the sunset ♪

18:14.587 --> 18:18.683
♪ That moment is still lingering ♪

18:18.683 --> 18:25.040
♪ When our eyes meet,
all vanish into nothing ♪

18:27.432 --> 18:33.883
♪ There seems to be a river
flowing through my heart ♪

18:34.071 --> 18:39.834
♪ Echoing with the constant gentleness
of the bright moon ♪

18:40.072 --> 18:42.989
♪ Looking back
among fleeting and everlasting moments ♪

18:42.989 --> 18:45.895
♪ We embrace as we look around ♪

18:45.895 --> 18:51.400
♪ Each sound is a promise of forever
to a lifetime ♪

18:51.400 --> 18:57.789
♪ It seems like you linger in my dreams
countless times ♪

18:57.813 --> 19:03.389
♪ Whenever I hear you,
my heart flutters a thousand times ♪

19:03.389 --> 19:07.013
♪ Birds fly past spring and autumn
once again ♪

19:07.013 --> 19:10.675
♪ The splendid world still remains ♪

19:10.792 --> 19:14.664
♪ Gifting us freedom ♪

19:14.664 --> 19:19.260
♪ We ferment each other into wine ♪

19:20.328 --> 19:26.757
♪ Within the intoxication, I can feel ♪

19:26.757 --> 19:30.678
♪ Your voice drifts across my heart ♪

19:30.702 --> 19:38.682
♪ Drifting through my life with no end ♪

20:03.848 --> 20:06.428
(Go out for a walk?)

20:08.749 --> 20:10.249
Quietly.

20:11.429 --> 20:13.529
I will go upstairs and get ready.

20:25.989 --> 20:28.209
The air is so fresh after the rain.

20:29.029 --> 20:30.769
It was drizzling just now.

20:34.148 --> 20:35.249
Are you happy?

20:37.429 --> 20:40.368
Yes. Very happy.

20:42.709 --> 20:46.324
- Where did you go?
- Just went out and walked a while.

20:46.348 --> 20:48.364
To see what's good to eat and
where can we have fun.

20:48.388 --> 20:51.009
So I can take you there
after you wake up.

21:08.908 --> 21:11.648
See, there's a lovely island.

21:18.669 --> 21:19.848
That one?

21:23.628 --> 21:26.568
Can you tell what's behind the island?

21:30.388 --> 21:31.568
You want to know?

21:46.789 --> 21:48.808
Wow! So beautiful!

21:52.068 --> 21:53.408
Careful!

21:56.148 --> 21:57.148
See.

22:00.029 --> 22:02.009
That island.

22:02.828 --> 22:05.169
Now you know what's behind there.

22:05.828 --> 22:07.249
I know now.

22:08.229 --> 22:09.249
See!

22:57.429 --> 22:59.568
Coming!

23:00.749 --> 23:03.209
- Zhou Zheng, hurry.
- Come on, come on, come on.

23:03.348 --> 23:05.009
You throw it so far.

23:06.269 --> 23:09.289
- Ready to jump.
- One, two, three, go!

23:12.628 --> 23:14.648
- Let's go
- You first.

23:17.108 --> 23:18.489
So fun!

23:19.789 --> 23:22.804
Wait, where is my sister?
Where did she go?

23:22.828 --> 23:24.765
- I will go look for her.
- Wait.

23:24.789 --> 23:27.209
You go down first!

23:28.749 --> 23:30.128
Splash water on him.

23:35.868 --> 23:37.249
Are there any balls?

23:40.068 --> 23:43.524
Zhou Zheng, what are you doing?
You don't take off your clothes or swim.

23:43.548 --> 23:45.205
- That's true.
- You arranged us to swim.

23:45.229 --> 23:46.804
But now you don't do anything.

23:46.828 --> 23:50.445
Juemei, have you grown wings or a tail?
Why aren't you swimming?

23:50.469 --> 23:52.328
Exactly.

23:52.548 --> 23:54.169
Can't I just warm-up?

24:00.789 --> 24:04.284
- Sorry I am late.
- Baby.

24:04.308 --> 24:05.308
Quickly, come.

24:09.640 --> 24:10.769
He took off.

24:17.229 --> 24:19.689
- Good body shape!
- Wow.

24:20.868 --> 24:23.328
You see, he just wants to show off.

24:27.269 --> 24:28.989
- Wow!
- Cool!

24:28.989 --> 24:32.328
- A large black fish.
- That's cool.

24:32.749 --> 24:33.848
Go!

24:34.588 --> 24:38.405
Yiru, you should thank Xiaoxing. We
can't get such benefits without her.

24:38.429 --> 24:40.364
- What are you talking about?
- Thank you, Xiaoxing.

24:40.388 --> 24:44.749
I was wondering why he was delaying.
He was waiting for someone, huh?

24:44.749 --> 24:48.604
- Keep your voice down. Embarrassing.
- There is something we don't know.

24:48.628 --> 24:50.884
Scheming boy, come here.

24:50.908 --> 24:52.868
- Coming.
- Coming.

24:52.868 --> 24:55.929
- You don't go swimming?
- No, I don't.

24:55.989 --> 24:57.564
- And you?
- Me neither.

24:57.588 --> 24:59.969
I'll go then.

25:02.269 --> 25:04.929
Feng Yasong, I'm coming!

25:07.068 --> 25:09.489
- So cold!
- The water is so cold.

25:12.469 --> 25:14.088
Hurry up!

25:16.308 --> 25:20.804
Dong Yiru, why my sister isn't here yet?
Is she with Mo Qingcheng?

25:20.828 --> 25:24.108
- I have to go and find her.
- No.

25:24.108 --> 25:26.169
Come here.

26:15.989 --> 26:18.808
Is that fine that we don't go swimming?

26:19.709 --> 26:22.689
They are too noisy. Let them have fun.

26:23.989 --> 26:26.289
It's dark now, anyway.

26:27.348 --> 26:29.088
I guess they will come back soon.

26:51.789 --> 26:54.608
So beautiful! So many stars!

26:55.548 --> 26:58.648
Normally, we can't see so
many stars in the city.

26:59.828 --> 27:01.729
Have you seen Sagittarius constellation?

27:03.469 --> 27:05.529
Which one is it?

27:06.709 --> 27:07.729
That one.

27:12.648 --> 27:13.724
Which one?

27:14.308 --> 27:15.969
Sit down.

27:18.029 --> 27:19.740
- Where?
- There.

27:20.296 --> 27:21.948
There, do you see?

27:22.536 --> 27:26.009
There's a triangle on top
and a quadrilateral at the bottom.

27:27.108 --> 27:31.328
I see. A quadrilateral on the bottom
and a triangle on top.

27:33.868 --> 27:35.648
What other constellations are there?

27:36.348 --> 27:37.489
Let me see.

27:40.108 --> 27:41.529
Let's lie down.

27:48.189 --> 27:49.189
There.

27:49.709 --> 27:51.568
In that direction, a bit farther away.

27:52.269 --> 27:56.888
- That one is the Scorpio constellation.
- Scorpio, what does it look like?

27:58.749 --> 28:01.408
- "S" shape.
- "S" shape?

28:04.348 --> 28:06.689
Like this. Do you see?

28:08.388 --> 28:10.489
I see. "S" shape.

28:11.269 --> 28:13.020
So beautiful.

28:13.669 --> 28:17.568
It's a pity I didn't bring my phone.
It would be nice to have some music.

28:23.189 --> 28:29.568
The last song you sang that day
was particularly beautiful.

28:31.229 --> 28:32.229
You like it?

28:35.669 --> 28:37.404
Actually that day,

28:37.949 --> 28:40.169
I sang it too serious.

28:41.189 --> 28:43.209
Is there any way not serious?

28:45.908 --> 28:47.128
Want to hear?

28:48.709 --> 28:50.408
How about you sing it without music?

28:53.640 --> 28:54.729
Okay.

29:03.429 --> 29:05.959
♪ Beyond the ferry bridge ♪

29:05.959 --> 29:13.648
♪ Fragrant grass spreading
across the eternal mountain ♪

29:16.108 --> 29:18.368
♪ Dream gone ♪

29:18.368 --> 29:24.489
♪ Geese come and go,
mountain changes to river ♪

29:26.308 --> 29:30.236
♪ I've believed
that this life was all a dream ♪

29:30.868 --> 29:35.009
♪ Awakening from intoxication,
realizing time flies in an instant ♪

29:37.868 --> 29:40.048
♪ Among old friends ♪

29:40.669 --> 29:42.364
♪ It's easy to encounter ♪

29:45.288 --> 29:47.769
♪ Hard to part ♪

30:03.515 --> 30:08.463
♪ Hey, why is it happening ♪

30:09.435 --> 30:12.143
♪ My heart is racing ♪

30:16.029 --> 30:22.009
- Dong Yiru, hurry up. I'm in a hurry.
- Slow down. I can't see the road.

30:22.548 --> 30:25.128
It's not your sister.

30:25.588 --> 30:28.729
Well, why in such a hurry?

30:29.189 --> 30:30.989
Your sister has already grown up.
She can't get lost.

30:30.989 --> 30:33.368
Go, quickly!

30:34.669 --> 30:40.044
- Gu Jia, what's wrong? Slow down!
- Dong Yiru, hurry up!

30:40.068 --> 30:44.685
What are you doing? I'm getting along
well with my idol happily.

30:44.709 --> 30:47.765
- But why did you call me back?
- I didn't drag you down today.

30:47.789 --> 30:51.324
After all, my sister didn't come today.
I am just worried.

30:51.348 --> 30:55.084
What could happen to your sister when
she's with someone else? She's an adult.

30:55.108 --> 30:57.009
Be mature.

30:58.469 --> 30:59.568
See.

31:03.108 --> 31:07.568
This cola is obviously just poured.
It's still cold.

31:11.068 --> 31:14.449
- Is it cold? Isn't it nice to drink?
- I don't want to talk to you.

31:15.868 --> 31:18.685
No, what are you doing, Gu Jia?

31:18.709 --> 31:20.925
I did just see this light
flicker off for a moment.

31:20.949 --> 31:23.084
Could you please stop being so
suspicious and paranoid?

31:23.108 --> 31:26.445
- Gu Sheng.
- Wait.

31:26.469 --> 31:30.289
You are impolite when they are here,
and you are awkward when they aren't.

31:30.469 --> 31:34.048
Here, play with me,
and I'll search with you, okay?

31:34.868 --> 31:38.205
- Play while searching.
- Play while searching. Is that okay?

31:38.229 --> 31:39.828
Okay, hurry up.

31:39.828 --> 31:42.084
- Play while searching.
- Play while searching.

31:42.108 --> 31:44.949
Look, how lively it is over there.
They must be enjoying the night.

31:44.949 --> 31:46.108
- How can they go back?
- There.

31:46.108 --> 31:48.568
Yes. See, there. Let's go.

31:51.029 --> 31:54.169
- Seems like they are gone.
- Gone.

31:56.229 --> 32:02.489
Wait, wait, don't turn it on.
What if they come back?

32:07.669 --> 32:09.929
- It's not right.
- What's wrong?

32:09.989 --> 32:14.048
We just sat in the courtyard.
We didn't really do anything.

32:14.908 --> 32:18.648
Hiding like this makes it seem as if
we've really done something wrong.

32:23.868 --> 32:26.969
Do you want coke? I'll pour you a glass.

32:28.068 --> 32:30.729
Keep your voice down, in case they hear.

32:32.108 --> 32:33.289
Okay.

32:56.388 --> 32:57.568
Sleepy?

33:00.669 --> 33:02.808
I just slept a little in the afternoon.

33:22.989 --> 33:25.009
I will lower the AC for you.

33:26.229 --> 33:28.328
It's comfortable
to sleep with the blanket.

34:01.189 --> 34:03.808
- Good night.
- Good night.

34:04.549 --> 34:05.808
Let's sleep.

34:18.589 --> 34:20.284
Actually swimming is quite easy.

34:20.308 --> 34:22.709
Tilt your head back, sweep with
your hands, and push with your feet.

34:22.709 --> 34:24.169
(Don't come back tonight.)

34:28.069 --> 34:30.928
(Sheng is asleep.
You go somewhere else to sleep.)

34:33.789 --> 34:35.649
What's wrong? Why are you laughing?

34:37.948 --> 34:43.368
Are you hungry? How about we find a
restaurant and have a late-night meal?

34:44.428 --> 34:46.049
Sure!

34:52.388 --> 34:55.725
My throat is a bit uncomfortable.
I may have a cold. Do you have medicine?

34:55.749 --> 34:57.444
I do. I will get it for you.

34:57.468 --> 34:59.908
- So you go first. I'll find you later.
- Okay.

34:59.908 --> 35:01.565
- I'll send you the address.
- Okay.

35:01.589 --> 35:04.528
Doudou, we also feel sick.
Let's go together.

35:04.669 --> 35:06.488
- I don't.
- You do.

35:06.589 --> 35:07.069
- Me?
- Go.

35:07.069 --> 35:08.928
- Let's go get some medicine.
- Go.

35:08.988 --> 35:11.049
- I will catch up with you later.
- Okay.

35:13.709 --> 35:18.848
- Why are they all sick?
- Maybe poor physical condition.

35:21.749 --> 35:23.769
In the afternoon,
I saw a restaurant over there

35:23.769 --> 35:25.964
with quite a few people.
The food should be good.

35:25.988 --> 35:27.769
How about we go there to eat?

35:28.428 --> 35:30.172
- Good idea.
- Let's go.

35:30.728 --> 35:31.868
Go.

35:38.028 --> 35:39.169
Wait.

35:41.388 --> 35:45.888
- What's wrong? You took it seriously?
- Why did you come back?

35:49.629 --> 35:52.729
- What's wrong, Dong Yiru?
- Something's happening.

35:57.508 --> 35:59.769
I thought you are really sick.

36:03.229 --> 36:06.565
If they notice it, you feel embarrassed,
and if they don't, you are impolite.

36:06.589 --> 36:11.408
- Something's happening.
- It's not good to stay long. Go.

36:11.468 --> 36:14.289
Let's go. Stop looking.

36:20.868 --> 36:25.245
Cold beverages in such cold weather?
I think you'll need that medicine.

36:25.269 --> 36:26.289
Cold?

36:27.948 --> 36:31.528
You are so annoying.

36:49.149 --> 36:53.125
Mr. Mo falls in love and
Zhou Zheng likes that girl.

36:53.149 --> 36:55.729
The only singles are you and me.

37:01.789 --> 37:03.516
Is there any place that we can play?

37:04.229 --> 37:05.689
Around here?

37:06.348 --> 37:07.928
Seems like nothing.

37:08.988 --> 37:13.928
Taking this vacation is so uneventful.
A day won't pass by like this, right?

37:15.948 --> 37:20.408
No, it's still two hours to pass.

37:22.388 --> 37:25.645
No, we must do something to do
if everyone else has already.

37:25.669 --> 37:28.448
We can't just go back to sleep
like this. It would be such a waste.

37:35.388 --> 37:36.448
What's wrong?

37:36.988 --> 37:39.368
Forget about it. I don't want to go now.

37:39.988 --> 37:41.888
I'd rather stay with you!

37:43.149 --> 37:46.569
You've said everything. Impressive.

37:51.348 --> 37:54.569
Bachelors are not suitable for
couple activities.

37:59.388 --> 38:03.649
Haven't you thought
of having a boyfriend?

38:04.789 --> 38:10.888
- You are single, too. Why rush me?
- Me? I don't have time.

38:11.308 --> 38:12.648
I have time?

38:12.648 --> 38:15.565
You three are busy with your own things,
leaving the recording studio to me.

38:15.589 --> 38:19.408
So I need to be dedicated to the studio.
I have time?

38:19.828 --> 38:22.364
And we didn't even bring any medicine
with us when we went out.

38:22.388 --> 38:24.804
I'm in this situation purely because of
being delayed by you guys.

38:24.828 --> 38:30.049
- I would be guilty if you say this.
- Then you better be guilty.

38:30.868 --> 38:34.320
You owe me.
Remember to repay it in the future.

38:34.344 --> 38:40.049
Okay, I'll remember this favor.
I won't forget it.

38:58.308 --> 39:00.928
Why are you looking at me?
Have you figured out how to repay it?

39:17.149 --> 39:18.689
So tasty.

39:19.908 --> 39:22.169
And this one also!

39:30.149 --> 39:33.169
You weren't full for dinner?
Why are you eating so much?

39:34.508 --> 39:35.868
No, no.

39:36.388 --> 39:41.408
This restaurant is so amazing.
I couldn't stop.

39:42.189 --> 39:44.528
I would probably gain
a lot of weight later.

39:45.109 --> 39:49.569
If you're afraid of gaining weight,
I'll go for a walk with you later.

39:49.629 --> 39:50.888
To help digest.

40:14.589 --> 40:18.528
You always took care of me
when we were in Yangshuo.

40:19.828 --> 40:20.968
Thank you.

40:23.388 --> 40:29.368
I wanted to treat you meal
after we were back to thank you.

40:29.428 --> 40:30.689
However,

40:31.428 --> 40:33.609
I never got a chance.

40:35.348 --> 40:37.328
How about let me treat

40:37.908 --> 40:39.089
this time?

40:39.468 --> 40:42.249
No, I've paid the bill.

40:43.749 --> 40:45.368
But,

40:47.468 --> 40:50.729
after coming back from Yangshuo,

40:51.709 --> 40:57.008
I also wanted to find a chance to drink
coffee or have a meal with you.

40:57.988 --> 41:02.289
I was afraid you might be too busy,
so I didn't dare to disturb you.

41:13.988 --> 41:15.569
But,

41:22.229 --> 41:24.888
but I want to see you.

41:29.069 --> 41:31.289
You see me now.

41:45.388 --> 41:48.808
Want a smoothie?
I see they have it here. I'll go buy it.

41:54.308 --> 41:55.769
It's okay.

42:14.189 --> 42:16.488
Didn't you catch a cold?

42:17.069 --> 42:18.328
We recovered.

42:23.948 --> 42:24.968
We recovered.

42:28.308 --> 42:32.245
- I will get some smoothies. Want some?
- Mango flavor, please.

42:32.269 --> 42:35.689
- We will go buy it.
- No, tonight it's on me.

42:36.388 --> 42:39.528
So I will go buy it.
You can sit here and wait.

42:40.269 --> 42:42.528
Aren't you sick? Still want smoothies?

42:43.789 --> 42:45.116
Such a coincidence.

42:45.789 --> 42:48.488
What coincidence? What's the point of
pretending now? She has left.

42:48.828 --> 42:52.085
- We encountered. Not to disturb you.
- That's true.

42:52.109 --> 42:53.725
What are you talking about?

42:53.749 --> 42:55.964
She wasn't full
so I just came with her to eat.

42:55.988 --> 43:00.729
Mo Qingcheng is all over his wife,
and doesn't care about her classmate.

43:08.749 --> 43:12.689
- Is it the wrong time for us to come?
- You are late to catch on.

43:12.908 --> 43:14.685
Should we leave now?

43:14.709 --> 43:17.769
And make her throw away the smoothies?

43:27.004 --> 43:32.112
♪ There is a voice
that soaks the green plums ♪

43:32.956 --> 43:37.904
♪ There is a voice
that wrinkles the blue sky ♪

43:38.834 --> 43:43.123
♪ Shedding an invisible spring rain ♪

43:43.123 --> 43:49.322
♪ The world is drunk at a timid moment ♪

43:50.648 --> 43:56.016
♪ We talk and laugh
as if we are holding hands ♪

43:56.956 --> 44:03.004
♪ We stay silent
like falling behind the sunset ♪

44:03.004 --> 44:07.100
♪ That moment is still lingering ♪

44:07.100 --> 44:13.457
♪ When our eyes meet,
all vanish into nothing ♪

44:39.676 --> 44:46.222
♪ You flow through my heart like a river ♪

44:46.396 --> 44:51.984
♪ Echoing with the constant gentleness
of the bright moon ♪

44:52.284 --> 44:55.452
♪ Looking back
among fleeting and everlasting moments ♪

44:55.452 --> 44:58.436
♪ We embrace as we look around ♪

44:58.460 --> 45:03.696
♪ Each sound is a promise of forever
to a lifetime ♪

45:03.804 --> 45:10.256
♪ You linger in my dreams
countless times ♪

45:10.396 --> 45:15.708
♪ Whenever I see you,
my heart flutters a thousand times ♪

45:15.708 --> 45:19.549
♪ Birds fly past spring and autumn
once again ♪

45:19.549 --> 45:23.045
♪ The splendid world still remains ♪

45:23.157 --> 45:26.844
♪ Gifting us freedom ♪

45:26.844 --> 45:31.763
♪ We ferment each other into wine ♪

45:32.949 --> 45:38.948
♪ Within the intoxication, I can feel ♪

45:38.972 --> 45:43.132
♪ Your voice drifts across my heart ♪

45:43.132 --> 45:50.896
♪ Drifting through my life with no end ♪
